Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Jirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you came today as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You should properly lock your front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That is really careless of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nii-san, we're out of shampoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,N-NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\fnGentium Book Basic\fs90\be5\pos(650,305)\c&HFDFEFA&\3c&H46A851&}It is Without a Doubt, in Bed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you two are really compatible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can overcome any obstacle with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha locked herself in her room and won't come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, she's going to miss school...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is about that, then you need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your little sister is right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking everywhere for you, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You-!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Konoe-senpai say anything after he saw me in my underwear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No reaction!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "boys' love?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it turn out like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dating Konoe-senpai, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru is madly in love with your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you should not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, your brother is going out with yours truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The birthmark on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a birthmark on his side, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in bed together, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In bed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's when she...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, Nii-san can't stand being touched by girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,His nose will start bleeding immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can overcome all obstacles with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to cheer for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you might become my little sister in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us get along, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzutsuki-senpai... No, Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, I want Subaru to experience love with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How about having a double date this coming Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Konoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not carelessly approach me from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a stun-gun for self-protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been specially customized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hit the right vital points with this‒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in possession of such a dangerous weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I must focus on protecting Ojou-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I cannot protect you as well. Please watch your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Konoe-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Jirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, just close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{No need to fill up}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{No need to fill up}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep an eye out for you, so feel free to change in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everything have to be so difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure took your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you aren't thinking about something bad about me, are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Konoe-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you teach me how to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that good of a swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It is fine with me, Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people here, but if anything happens, Jirou will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ojou-sama says so... I'm counting on you, Jirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was up with Konoe just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many years it has been since we last came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, when we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru and I were once kidnapped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kana-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanted a ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The incident was resolved swiftly, and all the criminals were caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of that incident, my movements have been restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru felt responsible for that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it was my own fault that I was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She could not protect her mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was only a child back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, the distance between us only grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Similar to how you have gynophobia, Subaru has her own weaknesses as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Weaknesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's stop the chit-chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop sitting around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are supposed to be my lover, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I showed him my good side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The real battle begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's come up with a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru, I am a bit thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go with Jirou and buy some drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I am not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are on good terms with Kureha, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous. I got into a scuffle with my father yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I told him that you pushed me down in the science room and got a nosebleed from touching my breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So he said, "Bring me that four-eyed bastard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll rip him to shreds and then lynch him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe, go get an employee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't flip out. If I had, it would've been bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't flip out. If you had made me, it would have been bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stay by my side?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stand by me," means, "I want you to be beside me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? Isn't it romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's too much of a hurdle for a five-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Know this, Kinjirou. Your name has the character for "close" in it for a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I want you to say to someone, "Stay by my side."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother, Kureha, or someone you believe to be precious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Become a man that can say, "I will become strong and I will protect you, so stay by my side."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stay by my side." That is a promise from Sakamachi Jirou to Sakamachi Kinjirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, have I still kept our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just met an acquaintance of mine in the gardens of Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you. Stop making such crude jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel better now, let's meet up with Ojou-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a bit of time has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone told me to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello, hello, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're pretty composed aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though your precious master has disappeared, Konoe Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to ask you one more time, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am only going to say this once, so listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are speaking to the venerable Kidnapping Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come here in ten minutes ,'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you call the police, it's game over. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault, I cannot allow Jirou to come in harm's way because of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man, youth is great! What good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well then, take care, little butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Subaru's reacting the same way I do when I touch a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru has her own weaknesses as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe, are you scared of blades?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me‒Did the same thing happen in the previous kidnapping incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ever since that incident, my body loses its strength whenever I see a weapon with a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a defective butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only was I not born as a male, but on top of that, I have a huge fear of bladed objects...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be strange for someone who is not able to protect her master to work as a butler...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I still want to remain as her butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make sure to save your sister, so wait here‒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Konoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything you ask afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are behind that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have some fun before that little butler arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So his target is Konoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not much of a fighter, you shitty brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou... Jirou is‒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still standing after all these hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't take all those beatings since I was five to just go down after a few hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get back on my feet as many times as you want, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "game set" for you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I didn't want to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Konoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou, I'll take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty late, little butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to tremble in fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time we were here, you were shaking and cried your eyes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the sight of a knife startled you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You were shaking like crazy just like a pitiful little sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the culprit who kidnapped Konoe and Suzutsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But Suzutsuki said that they were all apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm different now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm not afraid of your knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, that was kind of cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru... Jirou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't eat any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ojou-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologizes, Ojou-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of my carelessness that you and Kureha-chan went through something so dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... a failure as a butler...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you rescued me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As your master, I would not be able to fire a butler as loyal as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kana-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm such a hopeless butler, may I stay by your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with me, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As a butler and as a friend, stay by my side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Understood, Ojou-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have some fight left in you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Konoe Nagare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Suzutsuki family's butler-in-chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he's my father's butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're awake now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your injuries are nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I did hold back after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit me with all you had!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant that I held back just enough to not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, the scenario was planned so that she would not get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Scenario," you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be clear, I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I hate you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure don't hold back, you brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll repeat myself as many times as you want, you fool of a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagare, you may leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, Kanade-ojousama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagare and Jirou-kun are pretty similar to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How exactly are we similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You both cherish your families.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Nagare is, well... overbearing and overprotective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For Nagare, Subaru is his only immediate family, so it is to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,His only family?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru's mother passed away when she was only five.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a miracle that she even managed to give birth to Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you told me before, girls can't become butlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The members of my family followed this tradition, but Subaru rebelled against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that did not need a new mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been scary for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought of her mother disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that why she was so desperate to become a butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sincerely sorry to have dragged you into this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that there might have been an improvement if she came into contact with someone similar to herself, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what today's kidnapping incident was about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are correct, Jirou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice was you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you, Subaru can stay as my butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not care much about Konoe's father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it because I love Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true. Subaru was my first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for becoming my butler's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirou, I am coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you "would do anything I ask", didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I did but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You rescued Suzutsuki, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not defective anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I was afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I would never see you again when he tried to stab you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that Jirou, the first friend I made at school, might die on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Even if you apologize, I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Become a man who can say, "I will become strong and I will protect you, so stay by my side."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I promise I will become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Konoe-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Onee-sama that Nii-san might be holding Konoe-senpai in his arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Suzutsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To tempt Konoe-senpai even though you're already going out with Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going out with Ojou-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Laying your hands on Kana-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure look pretty energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You framed me again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have a bad reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, come with me. You're a being held hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that gynophobia of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can resist it if I only grab your sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is happening because of all that nonsense you told them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am telling the truth as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru really was my first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When all is said and done, girls are still scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.43,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Konoe what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am "servicing" my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This does not embarrass me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can I keep my precious "parts" tucked away?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, take off your clothes and throw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Mayo Chiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the fourth story:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stare so much...
